Package prototype.commodities.tests

Interface Summary
TechnicalTestInterface The TechnicalTestInterface is a standard interface for all of the technical tests.
 

Class Summary
MovingAverage MovingAverage calculates the moving average on a set of data.
MovingAverageExponential MovingAverageExponential calculates the moving average on a set of data.
MovingAverageExponentialTest The MovingAverageExponentialTest performs the moving average test using exponential factoring for a commodity.
MovingAverageTest The MovingAverageTest performs the moving average test for a commodity.
MovingAverageTriangle MovingAverageTriangle calculates the moving average on a set of data.
MovingAverageTriangleTest The MovingAverageTriangleTest performs the moving average test using exponential factoring for a commodity.
OpenInterestTest The OpenInterestTest performs the Open Interest test for a commodity.
Recommendation Recommendation contains a test's recommendation on what action to take with a commodity (buy/sell).
StatsAbstract The StatsAbstract contains methods used by all statistics classes within technical tests.
StochasticKDExponentialTest The StochasticKDExponentialTest performs the stochastic oscillator test where the oscillator (%K) is compared to a exponential moving average (%D) of the oscillator.
StochasticKDTest The StochasticKDTest performs the stochastic oscillator test where the oscillator (%K) is compared to a moving average (%D) of the oscillator.
StochasticKDTriangleTest The StochasticKDTriangleTest performs the stochastic oscillator test where the oscillator (%K) is compared to a triangle moving average (%D) of the oscillator.
StochasticTest The StochasticTest performs the stochastic oscillator test where the oscillator is compared to crossing a percentage level on both the high end (eg 80%) and the low end (eg 20%).
TechnicalTestAbstract The TechnicalTestAbstract implements the common methods of the TechnicalTestInterface.
TestIdentifier  
TestManager The TestManager class controls what tests are available to the system and how they are accessed.
